title: Ebro In The Morning - Latto Talks to Ebro about Big Energy + The Jussie Smollett Conviction
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 3/11/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Jussie Smollett conviction, the new Shenseea album (29), and Latto and Ebro Talk Big Energy. (44)

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
